{"id":277080,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ferris_Bueller%27s_Day_Off","text":"\"Ferris Bueller's Day Off\" is a 1986 American teen comedy movie set in Chicago, Illinois. It was produced by John Hughes and Tom Jacobson and was directed by Hughes.\nTV show.\nThere was a TV show on NBC in 1990 called \"Ferris Bueller\", which was a prequel to the movie. Charlie Schlatter played Ferris Bueller; Jennifer Aniston played his sister. The Bueller family lived in Los Angeles instead of Chicago.","categories":[],"infobox_types":["movie"],"annotations":[{"uri":"United_States","surface_form":"American","offset":37},{"uri":"Teen_movie","surface_form":"teen","offset":46},{"uri":"Comedy_movie","surface_form":"comedy movie","offset":51},{"uri":"Chicago","surface_form":"Chicago","offset":71},{"uri":"Illinois","surface_form":"Illinois","offset":80},{"uri":"John_Hughes_(producer)","surface_form":"John Hughes","offset":109},{"uri":"NBC","surface_form":"NBC","offset":198},{"uri":"Ferris_Bueller_(TV_series)","surface_form":"Ferris Bueller","offset":218},{"uri":"Prequel","surface_form":"prequel","offset":247},{"uri":"Charlie_Schlatter","surface_form":"Charlie Schlatter","offset":269},{"uri":"Ferris_Bueller","surface_form":"Ferris Bueller","offset":294},{"uri":"Jennifer_Aniston","surface_form":"Jennifer Aniston","offset":310},{"uri":"Los_Angeles","surface_form":"Los Angeles","offset":374},{"uri":"Chicago","surface_form":"Chicago","offset":397}]}